 2018-08892018-06-22,  ,  ,  ,  INAC
ActIndian Act
SubjectAdministration and Control of Reserve Land Beardy's and Okemasis Indian Reserve No. 96 & 97-B, Saskatchewan ** Transfer **
PrecisOrder (1) consenting to the exercise of the power of Saskatchewan to take a portion of land in BEARDY'S and OKEMASIS INDIAN RESERVE NO. 96 & 97-B, Saskatchewan, pursuant to subsection 35(1) of the Indian Act; and (2) authorizing, in lieu of such taking, the transfer of administration and control of the required lands, pursuant to subsection 35(3) of the Indian Act.
RegistrationRegistration: UNR/
